                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">The Importance of Drinking Water: A Key to Good Health</h1>
                <p class="lead">Water is often called the elixir of life—and for good reason. It plays a critical role in almost every function of the human body. Despite its importance, many of us don’t drink enough water daily. Let’s explore why staying hydrated is essential and how it impacts our overall well-being.</p>
                
